Interface JHelpAnimation.Interpolation

  • Enclosing class:
    JHelpAnimation

    public static interface JHelpAnimation.Interpolation
    An interpolation.
    It is a function f, that
    [0, 1] -f-> [0, 1]
    f(0) = 0
    f(1) = 1
    f is strictly increase in [0, 1]
    f continues in [0, 1]

    JHelp
